
%h1 Welcome to Tribble

- @posts.each do |post|
  = link_to image_tag(post.thumbnail.url(:thumb).to_s), post
  %h2= link_to post.title, post
  %p
  Created by:
  = link_to "#{post.user.first_name} #{post.user.last_name}", user_path(post.user)
  %p
  = post.comments.count
  Comments
  %p
  = post.get_likes.size
  Likes
  %p
  = post.get_dislikes.size
  Dislikes
